rows.label: tlk45370151_04_msg0001
rows.name:
We may have avoided war with Invidia,
but the underlying issues have not
been solved.

rows.label: tlk45370151_04_msg0002
rows.name:
The fact remains that our relationship
with Invidia is more strained than ever
after the Temperantia incident.

rows.label: tlk45370151_04_msg0003
rows.name:
At this rate, when the life of the
Superbia Divine Beast reaches its inevitable
end, Gula will be our only refuge...

rows.label: tlk45370151_04_msg0004
rows.name:
I would like to avoid resorting to war
as much as anyone, but I am failing to
envision a peaceful solution...
